name: amazonaws-com-pinpoint-email-connector
description:
Amazon Pinpoint Email Service  This document contains reference information for
the Amazon Pinpoint [https://aws.amazon.com/pinpoint] Email API, version 1.0.
This document is best used in conjunction with the Amazon Pinpoint Developer
Guide [http://docs.aws.amazon.com/pinpoint/latest/developerguide/welcome.html].

The Amazon Pinpoint Email API is available in the US East (N. Virginia), US West
(Oregon) and the EU (Ireland) Regions at the following endpoints:

 *   US East (N. Virginia): email.us-east-1.amazonaws.com 
   
   
 *   US West (Oregon): email.us-west-2.amazonaws.com 
   
   
 *   EU (Ireland): email.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com
